{"text_id":115242,"tokens":["In"," this"," paper",","," the"," author"," addresses"," the"," problem"," of"," general","izing"," skills",","," which"," is"," a"," longstanding"," issue"," in"," reinforcement"," learning","."," The"," author"," proposes"," a"," solution"," that"," uses"," semi","-","supervised"," reinforcement"," learning",","," where"," a"," proxy"," task"," is"," used"," to"," help"," learn"," a"," general"," purpose"," policy","."," The"," proxy"," task"," is"," a"," board"," game",","," Chain","mail",","," which"," provides"," a"," somewhat"," random"," aspect"," to"," the"," actions",","," making"," it"," a"," suitable"," training"," ground"," for"," a"," general"," purpose"," agent","."," The"," paper"," is"," well","-","written",","," and"," the"," proposal"," has"," promise",","," but"," there"," are"," some"," significant"," challenges"," in"," actually"," implementing"," this"," approach","."," One"," significant"," challenge"," is"," that"," Chain","mail"," has"," a"," large"," number"," of"," states"," and"," actions",","," which"," means"," that"," for"," most"," tasks"," the"," agent"," would"," have"," to"," rely"," on"," observed"," information"," about"," the"," current"," state","."," This"," means"," that"," there"," would"," not"," be"," much"," learn"," from"," exploration",","," and"," the"," agent"," would"," need"," to"," depend"," on"," the"," initial"," state",","," which"," is"," already"," known"," to"," the"," agent","."," In"," addition",","," Chain","mail"," does"," not"," have"," a"," clear"," objective",","," which"," means"," that"," the"," agent"," would"," not"," be"," learning"," to"," optimize"," a"," meaningful"," reward"," signal","."," --"," Problem",":"," General","izing"," skills"," is"," a"," challenging"," problem"," in"," reinforcement"," learning",","," and"," the"," conventional"," solution"," is"," to"," use"," a"," specific"," task"," to"," train"," the"," agent","."," This"," approach"," has"," two"," major"," problems","."," First",","," it"," requires"," a"," lot"," of"," manual"," effort"," to"," design"," a"," task"," that"," captures"," the"," desired"," behavior",","," and"," even"," with"," that"," careful"," design",","," there"," may"," be"," significant"," variability"," between"," tasks",","," which"," makes"," it"," difficult"," to"," generalize"," the"," learned"," policy","."," Second",","," even"," with"," a"," well","-","designed"," task",","," there"," may"," be"," significant"," randomness"," in"," the"," environment",","," which"," makes"," it"," difficult"," to"," generalize"," the"," policy","."," Solution",":"," The"," author"," of"," this"," paper"," describes"," a"," solution"," that"," uses"," semi","-","supervised"," reinforcement"," learning"," to"," train"," a"," general"," purpose"," agent","."," The"," proposed"," approach"," uses"," a"," proxy"," task",","," Chain","mail",","," which"," provides"," a"," somewhat"," random"," aspect"," to"," the"," state","."," This"," allows"," the"," agent"," to"," generalize"," to"," new"," tasks"," by"," using"," a"," technique"," called"," experience"," replay","."," The"," author"," demonstrates"," that"," Chain","mail"," is"," a"," good"," proxy"," task"," by"," comparing"," the"," resulting"," policy"," to"," human"," players","."," --"," The"," paper"," General","izing"," Skills"," with"," Semi","-","Super","vised"," Reinforcement"," Learning"," describes"," a"," solution"," to"," the"," problem"," of"," general","izing"," skills"," using"," semi","-","supervised"," reinforcement"," learning","."," The"," author"," describes"," a"," proxy"," task",","," Chain","mail",","," that"," provides"," some"," level"," of"," randomness"," in"," the"," state"," space",","," which"," is"," intended"," to"," allow"," the"," agent"," to"," generalize"," to"," new"," tasks","."," The"," Chain","mail"," game"," is"," played"," on"," a"," grid"," where"," markers"," represent"," combatants"," and"," boxes"," represent"," terrain","."," At"," the"," start"," of"," the"," game",","," two"," generators"," choose"," two"," boxes"," and"," swap"," their"," positions","."," The"," generators"," are"," initially"," chosen"," by"," the"," agent",","," and"," the"," generators"," follow"," a"," random"," walk","."," The"," action"," space"," for"," Chain","mail"," is"," very"," large",","," and"," even"," with"," experience"," replay",","," the"," algorithm"," is"," not"," able"," to"," converge"," to"," a"," good"," policy","."," The"," author"," describes"," an"," alternate"," strategy"," that"," reduces"," the"," state"," space",","," which"," allows"," the"," algorithm"," to"," achieve"," better"," performance","."," The"," author"," also"," describes"," experiments"," using"," the"," learned"," policy"," to"," play"," other"," unrelated"," games",","," which"," the"," author"," attributes"," to"," the"," increased"," generalization"," of"," the"," policy","."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"dolly","label":1}